      "text": "Be a little proper, they say."
    },
    {
      "start": 951.12,
      "end": 952.54,
      "text": "사람들은 말하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 952.92,
      "end": 954.7,
      "text": "Be a little proper 하라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 955.44,
      "end": 957.1,
      "text": "적절히 행동하라고."
    },
    {
      "start": 958.08,
      "end": 961.28,
      "text": "Speak a little softer, they say."
    },
    {
      "start": 962.02,
      "end": 964.76,
      "text": "그리고 좀 더 부드럽게 말하라고 하죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 964.96,
      "end": 966.5,
      "text": "Speak a little softer."
